collectionMetadata.name: Age-standardised incidence rate of acute myocardial infarction by gender
collectionMetadata.description:
The table/figure shows the age-standardised incidence rate of acute myocardial infarction in Singapore with a breakdown by gender.

The rates are expressed as per 100,000 residential population and standardised to the Segi World Population.

The numbers will be updated annually due to ongoing retrospective case collection.
